reinforce the loyalty of the army.

114
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:56,320
Here comes Great Lady General.

115
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:13,880
Greetings from Chenyue of Feng Family.

116
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:29,320
