177
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:24,510
Now, I’m in Wind City,

178
00:14:24,830 --> 00:14:26,080
I need to learn from

179
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,560
all of you.

180
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:31,710
